******************* WARNING *******************

The files contained in this directory house the 
embedded database files.  Deleting or tampering
with these  files  will result in complete data
loss of all messages,  file information,  users
and any other information stored within the DB.

This directory should be added to a  backup set
or frequently copied to another location.  When
performing a backup or upgrade, you should only
use  the  tools  provided by the OpenTelegard/2 
distribution.  You may  also  safely copy these 
files to  another location provided the  OpenTG 
software is not running  or using the database.

The  OpenTelegard/2 Project  is not responsible
for any data loss what-so-ever! Please read the
LicenseAgreement that accompanied this software

***********************************************
